From SURF_DEEP

ale=1./(2.*c*ugr*sumi0)/sqrt(6.28318)*1.e-15

Initially:
sum_i0 =g/cm**3*km
c= km/s
ugr=km/s

Green function spectrum ale = s**2/km**2*cm**3/g/km  = s**2*10**(-15) s**2/g

spectrum of force g*cm/s**2*s 

spectral_amplitude = force*ale =cm*s

displacement = spectral_amplitude*d(omega) = cm
-------------------------------------------------
           al(j)=suml*ampl(j)*aM*const1
           az(j)=sumr*ampr(j)*aM*const1
const1= 1.E-07

From cm to nanometers: nanometr =10.E-09 m; 10.E-07 sm
